@dev Retrieve all NFTs base token uri
@dev Set the base token uri for all NFTs

@dev Retrieve all NFTs base token uri
@dev Set the base token uri for all NFTs

typeDescriptions.typeString: function (string memory,string memory) pure returns (string memory)

baseTokenURI().details: Retrieve all NFTs base token uri

getRelinquishmentToken(address).details: Retrieve the ownership transfer key preset by a current owner to a new owner preTransferOwnership method must be called prior to calling this method

isOwner(address).details: check if an address is one of the owners

preTransferOwnership(address).details: Allows any current owner to relinquish its part of control over the contract

params._newOwner: address of the futur new owner

returns._relinquishmentToken: bytes32 ownership transfer key for msg.sender => _newOwner

setBaseTokenURI(string).details: Set the base token uri for all NFTs

tokenURI(uint256).details: Retrieve the uri of a specific token

params._tokenId: the id of the token to retrieve the uri of

returns._0: computed uri string pointing to a specific _tokenId

transferOwnership(bytes32,address).details: Allows any current owner to definitively and safely relinquish its part of control over the contract to a new address

preTransferOwnership(address).notice: the calling contract owner must call this method to get the `relinquishmentToken`  prior calling `renounceOwnership` method and definitively loose his ownership
